  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>This hotel is offered on a half board basis.</p>
<p>Each day an extensive continental breakfast buffet offering fresh fruit, sweet and savoury pastries and cakes and additional hot options are available. </p>
<p>The three-course evening meal with a rotating choice is served at the Restaurant Akashon, which has been awarded the Bib Gourmand Distinction by the Guide Michelin. Some dishes on the a la carte menu may have an additional supplement.</p>
<p>There is also self-service tea and coffee available throughout the day.</p>
<p>A Christmas Meal and New Years Gala Dinner is included.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
