  <description><![CDATA[<p>We are delighted to offer this wonderful modern, yet comfortable, hotel located at the foot of the <span>Aiguille du Midi cable car which is the highest cable car in France.</span></p>
<h2>Great location</h2>
<p><span>The Hotel Heliopic is a lovely modern yet comfortable hotel with a fantastic location in <a data-udi="umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a>. The hotel's interior is influenced by the surrounding mountains, and the stone and wood have been used to create a sustainable, cosy hotel. </span><span>Each of the bedrooms is furnished to a high standard - offering you a comfortable place to return to after a day of exploring the resort. </span></p>
<p><span>Skiing in France is renowned for the vast array of terrain which is within easy reach of the hotel, head up the Vallee Blanche for world renowned off piste skiing, it is recommended that you hire a guide to show you the best route down. Throughout the winter season, the hotel also offers a paid shuttle service to the ski areas. </span></p>
<h2>Soothing spa</h2>
<p>The hotel has a wonderful spa, which is open everyday for hotel guests only, a treat for skiers and non skiers alike. The spa has a cutting edge concept which has a number of hot areas with a sauna, two hammams and a jacuzzi linked by a warm ‘tiedipaerium’ to the cold area which includes an ice grotto and plunge pool. There's also a large indoor swimming pool and to fully rejuvenate, beauty treatments and massages are also available for a local fee. </p>
<h2>Fun for the whole family</h2>
<p>The large lobby in the heart of the hotel offers a variety of special hospitality areas which include an all day tea and coffee station, a multimedia area, home cinema, arcade games, bar and restaurant. Children are well catered for with their own play room and there's even a popcorn machine available as an apres ski snack.</p>]]></description>
