  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Classic Rooms </strong>are bright and comfortable, they are around 22m² and sleep two people.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>are around 25m² and can sleeps two adults and a child. The room is made up as a twin or double and has an additional single bed which is suitable for a child up to 12 years old.</p>
<p>Interconnecting rooms are available on request.</p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>All rooms have double or twin beds (please specify preference when booking)</li>
<li>En suite with a bath with a shower head attachment or shower room</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Balcony with mountain views</li>
<li>Satellite TV with English speaking channels and movie player</li>
<li>Linen and towels</li>
<li>Bath robes and slippers</li>
<li>Toiletries</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Tea &amp; coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Telephone</li>
<li>Radio</li>
<li>Hair dryer</li>
<li>Kettle</li>
<li>Daily housekeeping is included</li>
<li>Baby cots and bed linen are available on request</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
